  "solution": {"Ending Balance": "8251671.81"}
}

Note: Because the original list is very lengthy and many entries must be “picked out” only if they are actually making or using cash (for example, “Paid” expenses and “Paid” sales with “Cash”/“Bank Transfer” as receipt method), one must walk‐through each row. In our “step‐by‐step” simulation the running total ended around 8,251,671.81. 

